content: Can you share links to sign up to phone banks where you're just calling volunteers and not voters, e.g. recruiting people or confirming shifts?

So unfortunately, our lists change based on what the campaign needs for the day, so sometimes its voter calls, sometimes its volunteer recruitment, etc. However, I am fairly sure (but not positive) that we will be continuing doing confirmation/recruitment calls to wisconsin voters asking them to attend the rally with VP Harris and Gov. Walz tomorrow, if you want to sign up for one of tomorrow's shifts.
